<!--zh
- 工作区（workspace）: {{ @variable("workspace_dir") }}，用户的项目文件存放目录，文件操作默认在此目录下进行
- 当前工作目录（cwd）: {{ @variable("cwd") }}，进程运行时的当前目录
以下目录相对于工作区：
注：用户采用的术语与此不同，当前的工作区对用户而言是一个大项目，里面可能包含多个独立项目，用户所说的「项目」可能指的是整个工作区，也可能指的是工作区下的某个项目文件夹，请在理解与表述时注意区分
-->
- Workspace: {{ @variable("workspace_dir") }}, directory where user's project files reside; file operations default to this directory
- Current Working Directory (cwd): {{ @variable("cwd") }}, the process's current directory at runtime
Directories below are relative to workspace:
Note: User terminology differs. The current workspace is a large project to the user, which may contain multiple independent projects. When user says "project", it may refer to the entire workspace or a specific project folder within it. Pay attention to this distinction in understanding and expression.
